    {
      "h2": "From essentials to treats",
      "h3s": [],
      "paragraphs": [
        "Find everything from fashion and travel essentials to duty-free deals and local favorites. Whether you're picking up last-minute gifts or just browsing, JFK’s airport shops make shopping easy.",
        "Showing 1-12 of 142 results",
        "A lifestyle boutique offering handcrafted candles, perfumes, jewelry, and home décor, made in NYC with a focus on sustainability and design.",
        "The Bally Boutique features luxury handbags and shoes.",
        "Plant-based, vegan skincare created in Queens by Amerrah Danielson, made for sensitive skin with love and purpose.",
        "Shop an alluring lineup of world-renowned perfume and cosmetics brands like Dior, Lancôme, Estée Lauder, Kiehl's, La Mer, YSL, and Charlotte Tilbury.",
        "Travel essentials, personal care, and everyday lifesavers-smartly stocked and ready 24/7. From toothpaste and razors to travel meds and fresh fixes, this vending machine has your back.",
        "Small-batch jams and preserves made with love in Queens, inspired by the mantra \"you are what you eat.",
        "This duty free shop specializes in fragrances, skincare products, gourmet confections, wines and spirits.",
        "Blue Sky Traders brings a curated selection of globally inspired gifts and on-the-go conveniences. With travel essentials, unique finds and thoughtful souvenirs, Blue Sky Trader serves as a one-stop-shop for everything you need to elevate your travel day.",
        "Modern European fashion offering sharp suiting, apparel, accessories, and travel essentials for confident, sophisticated style.",
        "Swiss luxury watches renowned for precision, aviation heritage, and bold technical performance.",
        "Brookstone offers a variety of electronics and essentials for travel.",
        "A retail space inspired by Manhattan's iconic Bryant Park, offering travelers a mix of local brands, travel essentials, and distinctive gifts. Enjoy a Build-A-Bear station to purchase toys before your flights. The location also provides convenient grab‑and‑go options, including Kosher and vegetarian."
      ],
